  "body": "Tested on mac 10.9, 7c0a18edb58c46a68bdf524dc2bf3e7edf61dba2\n\n**You can use [eth-event-tests](https://github.com/debris/eth-event-tests) repository to reproduce these issues faster**\n- When node is not mining, events are 'not saved'. Scenario:\n  - create contract\n  - mine\n  - stop mining\n  - call contract function, which triggers an event\n  - call contract function, which triggers an event\n  - start mining\n  - call to eth_getLogs returns empty array\n\n_tested on private network_\n\neth_getLogs request:\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"method\": \"eth_getLogs\",\n  \"params\": [\n    {\n      \"fromBlock\": \"earliest\",\n      \"topics\": [\n        \"bcdfe0d5b27dd186282e187525415c57ea3077c34efb39148111e4d342e7ab0e\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"id\": 1\n}\n```\n",
